note bottom of Project
Project does not own an Issue collection in memory.
Issue.projectId records the project relationship.
Admin project detail returns project + participants only.
Non-admin project screens combine project detail with issue queries.
end note

note bottom of IssueDetailResult
availableActions carries workflow action names for the issue detail screen.
IssueController fills it when IssueWorkflowService is configured.
end note

